    "How does quicksort work?": "Â¿CÃ³mo funciona la clasificaciÃ³n rÃ¡pida?",
    "Pick pivot, partition elements\nRecursively sort partitions\n\nTime: Avg O(n log n), Worst O(nÂ²)": "Elija pivote, elementos de particiÃ³n\nOrdenar particiones recursivamente\n\nTiempo: Promedio O(n log n), Peor O(nÂ²)",
    "What is backtracking?": "Â¿QuÃ© es retroceder?",
